:name:
Umbra

:coretxt:
Affinity with shadows. With you they are not mere absent of light.

:cost:
1 Instinct

:req:
You have feeded on someone who has never seen the sun.

:1:
Move shadows. Can be used to terrify or to aid hiding. Can be used to create unnatural darkness.

:2:
Have shadows take a physical shape. They are able to aid you in a attack.

:3:
Take form of an shadow. 
Only sunlight, extremely bright light, or fire can harm you. 
You are able to move as you wish, only solid object can block your movement.


:tags:
Vampiric
VampiricMysticism
